FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/

# tubuy

`tubuy` is a **co-buying** API that people with a common interest at a commodity to buy it ***tugether.***  

`tubuy` believe's in **sharing is caring**
## API root [/api/]

### list all endpoints [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
                {
                        "users": "https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/api/users/",
                        "commodity": "https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/api/commodities/",
                        "contribution": "https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/api/contributions/"
                }
        }
## users [/api/users/]

