                }
        ]

### create a new user [POST]

a new user is created using a `username`, `email` and `password`

+ Request (application/json)

        {
                "username": "washington",
                "email":"washington@tubuy.io",
                "password": "washington"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                    "message": "user created"
            }


## commodities [/api/commodities/]

### list all commodities [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
                {
                            "url": "https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/api/commodities/1/",
                            "name": "buy pizza on terrific tuesday",
                            "requestor": "adam",
                            "price": "1000.00"
                },
                {
                            "url": "https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/api/commodities/2/",
                            "name": "buy ferrari",
                            "requestor": "eve",
                            "price": "200000.00"
                }
        ]

### create a new commodity [POST]

a new commodity is created using a `name` and the items' corresponding `price`

+ Request (application/json)

        {
                "name": "buy centum shares",
                "price": "200"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                    "url": "https://tubuy.herokuapp.com/api/commodities/2/",
                    "name": "buy centum shares",
                    "requestor": "josh",
                    "price": "200.00"
            }


## contributions [/api/contributions/]

### list all contributions [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
                {
                        "amount": "20.00",
                        "co_buyer": "eric",
                        "contributing_to": "buy pizza on terrific tuesday"
                },
                {
                        "amount": "500.00",
                        "co_buyer": "josh",
                        "contributing_to": "buy ferrari"
                },
                {
                        "amount": "10.00",
                        "co_buyer": "collin",
                        "contributing_to": "buy ferrari"
                }
        ]

### create a new commodity [POST]

a new contribution is created using `amount`

+ Request (application/json)

        {
                "amount": "10.00"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                    "amount": "10.00",
                    "co_buyer": "collin",
                    "contributing_to": "buy ferrari"
            }